Simple Calculator
A simple, responsive calculator built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This project replicates a basic calculator interface and functionality, allowing users to perform arithmetic operations with a clean, modern design.


Features
Basic arithmetic operations: addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division
Support for parentheses to manage order of operations
Percentage and square root functionality
Clear and delete (backspace) functions
Responsive and styled interface
Technologies Used
HTML for structure
CSS for styling and layout
JavaScript for functionality
Getting Started
Prerequisites
No prerequisites are required to run this project. All you need is a modern web browser.

